      • initialCenters

        public static InitialCenters<KDTree> initialCenters​(boolean notNear)
        Returns a method for initial cluster selection. It will select the mean of the nodes of the tree as centers. If there are more centers needed than nodes further points will be selected by the ReplaceEmptyCluster.farthest(boolean) method.
        Parameters:
        notNear - the parameter of ReplaceEmptyCluster.farthest(boolean)

      • nearestCenter2

        public static Function<Vector,​Vector> nearestCenter2​(java.util.List<Vector> centers,
                                                           Sum.Factory sum)
        Creates a function to determine the nearest center for points. For small number of centers it will iterate through all the vectors of centers. For larger number of centers it will use nearestCenter(List, Sum.Factory).

      • nearestCenter

        protected abstract void nearestCenter​(dog.giraffe.points.KDTree.NearestCenter nearestCenter,
                                      Vector point)
        Determines the nearest vector of this to the vector point. Leaf nodes iterates through all their vectors. Branch nodes use bounding boxes to exclude vectors from this.

        protected abstract boolean split​(java.util.Deque<KDTree> deque)
